== 制作 ==
[[File:Fran_Drescher_mirror.jpg|right]]（摄于1996年）开发并主演《美容师与野兽》]]

《美容师与野兽》源自法蘭·卓雪的构想<ref name="SourceTOK">{{Cite news | title = Actress Fits "High Maintenance" Profile | url = https://oklahoman.com/article/2571508/actress-fits-high-maintenance-profile | last = Davis | first = Sandi | date = 1997-02-07 | newspaper = The Oklahoman | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200224172308/https://oklahoman.com/article/2571508/actress-fits-high-maintenance-profile | archive-date = 2020-02-24}}</ref><ref name="Book3">{{Cite book | last = Drescher | first = Fran | url = https://archive.org/details/enterwhining00dres | title = Enter Whining | publisher = Regan Books | year = 1996 | isbn = 0-06-039155-3 | location = New York City | page = 264 | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}{{subscription required}}</ref>，自称是向音乐剧《[[國王與我|國王與我]]》致敬<ref name="Newspaper6">{{Cite news | last = Longsdorf | first = Amy | date = 1996-08-03 | title = Fran Drescher has just a sip of whine | work = The Morning Call | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200630234008/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54471417/p-a38/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54471417/p-a38/ | page = A37–A38 | deadurl = no | archive-date = 2020-06-30 | via = Newspapers.com}}{{subscription required}}</ref>。她还是本片的[[執行製作人|執行製作人]]，通过旗下高中甜心影业（{{lang|en|High School Sweethearts}}）参与制作<ref name="SourceVTY">{{Cite journal | title = The Beautician and the Beast | url = https://variety.com/1997/film/reviews/the-beautician-and-the-beast-1117436836/ | last = Levy | first = Emanuel | date = 1997-02-03 | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705063020/https://variety.com/1997/film/reviews/the-beautician-and-the-beast-1117436836/ | archive-date = 2018-07-05}}</ref><ref name="SourceDesert">{{Cite news | title = Film review: Beautician and the Beast, The | url = https://www.deseret.com/1997/2/11/20087103/film-review-beautician-and-the-beast-the | last = Vice | first = Jeff | date = 1997-02-07 | newspaper = Deseret News | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705234133/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/700000151/Beautician-and-the-Beast-The.html | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}</ref>。编剧托德·格拉夫对卓雪的提议很感兴趣，两人的幽默感类似，而且他已经“熟悉她的嗓音，知道她最适合哪些台词”，所以卓雪请他编剧<ref name="SourceTOK" />。电影制作期间，卓雪的要求就是剧本“完全适合（她）”，开拍后剧本还时有更改<ref name="Newspaper5">{{Cite news | date = 1996-11-06 | title = Beautician and the Beast | work = Calgary Herald | last = Portman | first = Jamie | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54471597/p-c5/ | deadurl = no | page = C5 | archive-date = 2020-07-02 | via = Newspapers.com | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200702044039/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54471597/p-c5/}} {{subscription required}}</ref>。[[罗杰·伯恩鲍姆|罗杰·伯恩鲍姆]]（{{lang|en|Roger Birnbaum}}）和[[彼得·马克·雅各布森|彼得·马克·雅各布森]]（{{lang|en|Peter Marc Jacobson}}）都是本片执行制作人，格拉夫和[[霍克·科奇|小霍华德·科奇]]（{{lang|en|Howard W. Koch, Jr.}}）任制片人<ref name="SourceVTY" />。

卓雪因[[情景喜剧|情景喜剧]]《[[天才保姆|天才保姆]]》（1993至1999年）扬名，打算借本片从电视圈进军影坛<ref name="SourceTOK" />。此前她在电影中只演过配角，处女作是1977年剧情片《[[週末夜狂熱|週末夜狂熱]]》，《美容师与野兽》是她首次主演<ref name="SourceCNNInteractive">{{Cite news | title = 'The Beautician and the Beast' close to Dresher's roots | url = http://edition.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/9702/07/beautician/ | last = Hillard | first = Gloria | archive-date = 2008-06-30 | date = 1997-02-07 | website = [[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080630204903/http://www.cnn.com/SHOWBIZ/9702/07/beautician/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。为避免观众不习惯她转战大银幕，卓雪以过去的电视演出为蓝本：“这是特殊的战略选择，让观众不会太难接受我出演其他人物。我希望能轻松过渡，避免他们一下难以接受”<ref name="SourceTOK" />。导演肯·卡皮斯（{{lang|en|Ken Kwapis}}）表示，卓雪的噪音、表演功底和特殊喜剧视角都会引来许多观众质疑，需要她克服并做好心理准备<ref name="SourceHB2">{{Cite news | title = Drescher hopes to show she's more than a 'Nanny' | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54472835/p-d-5/ | last = Strauss | first = Bob | date = 1997-02-04 | page = D5 | newspaper = Los Angeles Daily News | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | via = Newspapers.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200806115047/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54472835/p-d-5/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2020-08-06}} {{subscription required}}</ref>。在他看来，本片“比漫画还浪漫”，希望在向观众展示她“吵吵嚷嚷而又花里胡哨”的喜剧风格同时，也能表现她脆弱的一面<ref name="Newspaper10">{{Cite news | last = Beck | first = Marilyn | last2 = Smith | first2 = Stacy Jenel | date = 1996-10-10 | page = 55 | title = Hollywood: The King and Oy | newspaper = [[紐約每日新聞|New York Daily News]] | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54472985/p-55/ | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200703090356/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54472985/p-55/ | archive-date = 2020-07-03 | via = Newspapers.com}} {{subscription required}}</ref>。

蒂莫西·道尔顿参演的消息于1996年7月公布<ref name="Newspaper9">{{Cite news | last = Rodd | first = Catherine | date = 1996-08-16 | department = TVtimes | page = 9 | title = Information, please | newspaper = Edmonton Journal | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54473375/tvtimes-p-9/ | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190814211031/http://www.newspapers.com/image/473073062/ | archive-date = 2019-08-14 | via = Newspapers.com}} {{subscription required}}</ref>，卓雪起初的设想是请[[奇雲·格連|奇雲·格連]]出演鲍里斯，但档期有冲突<ref name="SourceTOK" />。卡皮斯认为道尔顿“魅力十足而且语调很温柔”<ref name="Newspaper10" />。笑匠劳拉·豪斯（{{lang|en|Laura House}}）认为，道尔顿在影坛已经颇有名气，选择他出演可以从侧面反映出卓雪的走红程度<ref name="Book4">{{Cite book | last = House | first = Laura | editor-last = Elwood | editor-first = Graham | editor-last2 = Mancini | editor-first2 = Chris | title = The Comedy Film Nerds Guide to Movies | chapter = Romantic Comedies | publisher = Morgan James Publishing | year = 2012 | isbn = 978-1-61448-221-5 | location = New York City | page = 149}}</ref>。《[[影音俱樂部|影音俱樂部]]》的威尔·哈里斯（{{lang|en|Will Harris}}）认为，《美容师与野兽》在道尔顿出演的电影中比较轻松搞笑。道尔顿在2014年接受采访时对参与本片演出颇感愉快，并称赞卓雪善于把握喜剧时机<ref name="SourceAVC">{{Cite journal | title = Timothy Dalton on Penny Dreadful, serenading Mae West, and being James Bond | archive-date = 2020-08-09 | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | url = https://tv.avclub.com/timothy-dalton-on-penny-dreadful-serenading-mae-west-1798269770 | last = Harris | first = Will | date = 2014-05-09 | journal = [[影音俱樂部|The A.V. Club]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200809202459/https://tv.avclub.com/timothy-dalton-on-penny-dreadful-serenading-mae-west-1798269770}}</ref>。卓雪自认拍摄期间就像大姐大般罩着道尔顿，不但在喜剧演出上协助他，还确保他有足够多的幽默台词<ref name="SourceTOK" />。

电影的取景地点包括：加利福尼亚州[[比佛利山|比佛利山]][[灰石豪苑|灰石豪苑]]（{{lang|en|Greystone Mansion}}）、[[捷克|捷克共和国]]首都[[布拉格|布拉格]]和[[錫赫羅夫城堡|錫赫羅夫城堡]]<ref name="SourceVTY" /><ref name="Book2">{{Cite book | last = White | first = Robert | title = Hollywood and the Best of Los Angeles | last2 = White | first2 = Phyllis | publisher = Hunter Publishing, Inc | year = 2011 | isbn = 1-58843-286-6 | location = Garsington | page = 273}}</ref>。其中捷克共和国取景镜头是在1996年秋摄制，卓雪在此期间还从[[托斯卡纳大区|托斯卡纳大区]]聘请厨师为她做饭<ref name="Newspaper6" />。彼得·里昂斯·科利斯特（{{lang|en|Peter Lyons Collister}}）负责摄影，乔恩·鲍尔（{{lang|en|Jon Poll}}）任剪辑师<ref name="SourceVTY" />。导演请来方言教练弗朗西·布朗（{{lang|en|Francie Brown}}）协助构建片中使用的斯洛文泽亚[[虛構語言|虛構語言]]<ref name="Book1">{{Cite book | last = Rogers | first = Stephen D. | title = The Dictionary of Made-Up Languages: From Elvish to Klingon, The Anwa, Reella, Ealray, Yeht (Real) Origins of Invented Lexicons | publisher = [[西蒙與舒斯特|Simon and Schuster]] | year = 2011 | isbn = 978-1-4405-2817-0 | location = Avon}}</ref><ref name="SourceComplex">{{Cite web | title = The 50 Worst Romantic Comedies: 14. The Beautician and the Beast (1997) | archive-date = 2018-08-05 | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | url = https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2012/12/50-worst-romantic-comedies/the-beautician-and-the-beast | last = Gallagher | first = Brenden | date = 2012-12-05 | website = Complex | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180805172501/https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/2012/12/50-worst-romantic-comedies/the-beautician-and-the-beast}}</ref>，其中包含[[捷克语|捷克语]]、[[俄语|俄语]]和[[匈牙利语|匈牙利语]]的显著影响<ref name="Book1" />。影片的摄制预算为1600万美元<ref name="SourceBOM">{{Cite web | title = The Beautician and the Beast (Summary) | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl323257857/weekend/ | website = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | deadurl = no | archive-date = 2020-08-19 | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200819165404/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl323257857/weekend/}}</ref>，[[剪輯|终剪]]版长107分钟<ref name="SourceRT" />。

== 主题 ==
据法蘭·卓雪透露，本片幽默之处在于把丰富多彩的美国人物与黑暗、压抑的城堡放在一起<ref name="SourceTOK" />。影评人[[伊曼纽尔·利维|伊曼纽尔·利维]]（{{lang|en|Emanuel Levy}}）称，片中以乔伊与鲍里斯相处指代西方民主与僵化低效[[共产主义|共产主义]]之间的文化冲突<ref name="SourceVTY" />，女主角将斯洛文泽亚推入“自由且技术先进的21世纪”<ref name="SourceVTY" />。史蒂芬·亨特（{{lang|en|Stephen Hunter}}）在《[[巴尔的摩太阳报|巴尔的摩太阳报]]》发文，称乔伊就像[[自由主义|自由主义]]的代言人，是忙碌且八卦现代女人的典型<ref name="SourceTBS">{{Cite web | title = Fran, keep your day job Review: It's a stretch, but 'Beautician and the Beast' does offer a measure of mirth. And, remember who's talking – you may want earplugs. | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | url = https://www.baltimoresun.com/news/bs-xpm-1997-02-07-1997038089-story.html | last = Hunter | first = Stephen | date = 1997-02-07 | newspaper = [[巴尔的摩太阳报|The Baltimore Sun]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705062915/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/1997-02-07/features/1997038089_1_fran-drescher-accent-dictator}}</ref>。评论将鲍里斯和[[约瑟夫·维萨里奥诺维奇·斯大林|约瑟夫·维萨里奥诺维奇·斯大林]]对比<ref name="SourceDesert" /><ref name="SourceTBS" /><ref name="SourceTVGuide">{{Cite web | title = The Beautician and the Beast: Reviewed by Maitland McDonagh | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | url = https://www.tvguide.com/movies/the-beautician-and-the-beast/review/132071/ | last = McDonagh | first = Maitland | journal = [[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]] | deadurl = no | archive-date = 2019-08-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190818003846/https://www.tvguide.com/movies/the-beautician-and-the-beast/review/132071}}</ref>，亨特认为道尔顿诠释的人物从衣着、发型、胡须甚至表情上都让人想到斯大林，所以这种对比很自然，而且人物决定朝民主方向迈进后形象也很快大变，尽显“狂野与疯狂”<ref name="SourceTBS" />。

部分影评人将《美容师与野兽》视为童话《[[美女与野兽|美女与野兽]]》的改编作品<ref name="SourceEmpire">{{Cite journal | title = Beauty And The Beast Review | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/beauty-beast-2-review/ | last = Semlyen | first = Nick De | date = 2017-03-16 | journal = [[帝國雜誌|Empire]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191206200304/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/beauty-beast-2-review/ | archive-date = 2019-12-06 | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}</ref><ref name="SourceTHR">{{Cite journal | title = 13 'Beauty and the Beast' Adaptations | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/13-beauty-beast-adaptations-985165 | last = Washington | first = Ariene | date = 2017-03-10 | journal = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705063208/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/13-beauty-beast-adaptations-985165 | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}</ref><ref name="SourceIGN">{{Cite web | title = Beauties and the Beast: 9 Other Filmed Versions of the Tale as Old as Time | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2017/03/16/beauties-and-the-beasts-9-other-filmed-versions-of-the-tale-as-old-as-time | last = Blumberg | first = Arnold T. | date = 2017-03-16 | website = [[IGN|IGN]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705133009/http://www.ign.com/articles/2017/03/16/beauties-and-the-beasts-9-other-filmed-versions-of-the-tale-as-old-as-time | archive-date = 2018-07-05}}</ref>，也有文章认为作品受《天才保姆》影响显著<ref name="SourceEW">{{Cite journal | title = Fools Rush In; The Beautician and the Beast | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | url = https://ew.com/article/1997/02/14/fools-rush-beautician-and-beast/ | last = Schwarzbaum | first = Lisa | date = 1997-02-14 | journal = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | archive-date = 2020-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200928084516/https://ew.com/article/1997/02/14/fools-rush-beautician-and-beast/ | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="Book6">{{Cite book | last = Monush | first = Barry | title = The Sound of Music FAQ: All That's Left to Know About Maria, the von Trapps, and Our Favorite Things | chapter = That Ever-Present ''Sound of Music'': Pop Culture References to the Musical | publisher = Hal Leonard Corporation | year = 2015 | isbn = 978-1-4803-6043-3 | at = Chapter 15 | location = Milwaukee}}</ref>。影片和音乐剧《国王与我》、《[[音乐之声|音乐之声]]》颇为相似，都聚-{焦}-文化和性别差异<ref name="SourceVTY" /><ref name="SourceHB1">{{Cite journal | title = The Beautician and the Beast | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G2-2505901772.html | date = 2008-01-01 | journal = Golden Movie Retriever | deadurl = yes | archive-date = 2018-06-30 | accessdate = 2018-06-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180630052612/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G2-2505901772.html}} {{subscription required}}</ref>。[[佩利媒体中心|佩利媒体中心]]（{{lang|en|Paley Center for Media}}）研究员巴里·莫努什（{{lang|en|Barry Monush}}）指出，片中乔伊用[[拉尔夫·劳伦|拉尔夫·劳伦]]床上用品制作服装的情节明显意指《音乐之声》<ref name="Book6" />。利维觉得本片就像“没有歌曲的歌舞片”<ref name="SourceVTY" />。还有评论将电影与[[恩斯特·劉別謙|恩斯特·劉別謙]]的《[[妮諾奇嘉|妮諾奇嘉]]》和《[[街角的商店|街角的商店]]》对比<ref name="SourceVTY" /><ref name="SourceSDR">{{Cite news | title = The Beautician and the Beast | url = https://www.sandiegoreader.com/movies/beautician-and-the-beast/# | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | last = Shepherd | first = Duncan | newspaper = San Diego Reader | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705063157/https://www.sandiegoreader.com/movies/beautician-and-the-beast/ | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}</ref>，音乐专栏作家大卫·赫希（{{lang|en|David Hirsch}}）称《美容师与野兽》配乐类似20世纪40年代电影<ref name="Book5">{{Cite book | last = Hirsch | first = David | editor-last = Deutsch | editor-first = Didier C. | chapter-url = https://archive.org/details/musichoundsoundt00didi/page/46/mode/2up | chapter = The Beautician and the Beast | title = MusicHound Soundtracks: The Essential Album Guide to Film, Television and Stage Music | publisher = Visible Ink Press | year = 2000 | isbn = 1-57859-101-5 | location = New York City | page = 46 | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}</ref>。卡特里娜与亚历克相恋，就像莎士比亚剧作《[[罗密欧与朱丽叶|罗密欧与朱丽叶]]》中的[[朱麗葉·凱普萊特|朱丽叶]]和[[羅密歐·蒙泰古|罗密欧]]<ref name="SourceMTVNews">{{Cite news | title = Eric's Bad Movies: The Beautician and the Beast (1997) | archive-date = 2019-09-16 | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | url = http://www.mtv.com/news/2759146/erics-bad-movies-the-beautician-and-the-beast-1997/ | last = Snider | first = Eric | date = 2008-05-01 | website = MTV News | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190916064319/http://www.mtv.com/news/2759146/erics-bad-movies-the-beautician-and-the-beast-1997/}}</ref><ref name="SourceRE">{{Cite web | title = The Beautician and the Beast | archive-date = 2020-10-04 | url = https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-beautician-and-the-beast-1997 | last = Ebert | first = Roger | author-link = 罗杰·伊伯特 | date = 1997-02-07 | website = RogerEbert.com | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201004022514/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-beautician-and-the-beast-1997 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，还有评论认为片头的动画场景是恶搞1959年电影《[[睡美人_(1959年電影)|睡美人]]》<ref name="SourceDesert" />。

