《美容师与野兽》的配乐由克利夫·艾德曼（{{lang|en|Cliff Eidelman}}）作曲，英国[[温布利|温布利]]{{lang|en|CTS}}录音室录制，19首曲目由伦敦都市管弦乐团（{{lang|en|London Metropolitan Orchestra}}）演奏<ref name="Source1">{{Cite web | title = AllMusic Review by Jason Ankeny | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | url = https://www.allmusic.com/album/beautician-and-the-beast-original-soundtrack-mw0000966314 | last = Ankeny | first = Jason | website = [[AllMusic|AllMusic]] | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705063422/https://www.allmusic.com/album/beautician-and-the-beast-original-soundtrack-mw0000966314}}</ref>。配乐包含[[俄罗斯古典音乐|俄罗斯古典音乐]]和[[圆舞曲|圆舞曲]]元素<ref name="Book5" /><ref name="Source1" />。艾德曼共创作17首曲目，剩下两首分别是[[皮埃尔·狄盖特|皮埃尔·狄盖特]]创作的《[[国际歌|国际歌]]》和杰里·格拉夫（{{lang|en|Jerry Graff}}）的《{{lang|en|J}}圆舞曲》（{{lang|en|"The J Waltz"}}）<ref name="Source1" />，其中《国际歌》增加合唱部分<ref name="Book5" />。本片预告片的配乐曲[[约翰·贝尔_(作曲家)|约翰·贝尔]]（{{lang|en|John Beal}}）作曲<ref name="SourceAppleMusic" />，但没有收入原声带唱片，后与贝尔的其他预告片配乐发行[[合輯|合輯]]<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="SourceAppleMusic">{{Cite web | title = Coming Soon: The John Beal Trailer Project, Vol. 1 | website = [[Apple_Music|Apple Music]] | deadurl = yes | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | url = https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/coming-soon-the-john-beal-trailer-project-vol-1/926304286 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705064543/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/coming-soon-the-john-beal-trailer-project-vol-1/926304286 | accessdate = 2018-07-05}}</ref>。

1997年2月11日，米兰唱片（{{lang|en|Milan Records}}）发行《美容师与野兽》的配乐[[CDDA|音频CD]]<ref name="Source2">{{Cite web | title = Releases | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | url = https://www.allmusic.com/album/beautician-and-the-beast-original-soundtrack-mw0000966314/releases | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705063428/https://www.allmusic.com/album/beautician-and-the-beast-original-soundtrack-mw0000966314/releases | website = AllMusic | deadurl = no}}</ref>，之后又在{{lang|en|[[Spotify|Spotify]]}}提供[[流媒体|-{zh-hans:流媒体点播;zh-hant:串流點播;}-]]<ref name="SourceSpotify">{{Cite web | title = The Beautician and the Beast | url = https://open.spotify.com/album/11yHXTipkV8RRwLdODWjON | website = [[Spotify|Spotify]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705063331/https://open.spotify.com/album/11yHXTipkV8RRwLdODWjON | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | accessdate = 2020-11-01}} {{subscription required}}</ref>。原声带评价不一，赫希称赞其中“迷人的老式浪漫曲调”<ref name="Book5" />，{{lang|en|[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]}}网站的杰森·安肯尼（{{lang|en|Jason Ankeny}}）认可艾德曼作曲时不依赖喜剧配乐中烂大街的甜蜜和多愁善感，但批评旋律沉重且没有重心，缺乏浪漫喜剧应该呈现的活泼与热情<ref name="Source1" />。

