== 发行和票房 ==
1997年2月4日，《美容师与野兽》在[[好莱坞|好莱坞]]首映<ref name="SourceGetty">{{Cite web | title = Premiere of "The Beautician and the Beast" | accessdate = 2018-07-05 | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | url = https://www.gettyimages.com/event/premiere-of-the-beautician-and-the-beast-75071145#/timothy-dalton-during-premiere-of-the-beautician-and-the-beast-at-in-picture-id134374417 | date = 1997-02-04 | deadurl = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705062818/https://www.gettyimages.com/event/premiere-of-the-beautician-and-the-beast-75071145 | website = [[盖帝图像|Getty Images]]}}</ref>。[[美國電影協會|美國電影協會]]在派拉蒙影业位于[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]的放映室审查后为本片评级[[美国电影分级制度|PG]]<ref name="SourceVTY" />。1997年2月7日，电影通过[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]在1801家剧院[[全國上映|全面上映]]<ref name="SourceRT" /><ref name="SourceVTY" /><ref name="SourceBOMTheaters">{{Cite web | title = Ken Kwapis | archive-date = 2015-10-16 | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Director&id=kenkwapis.htm&sort=maxtheaters&order=DESC&p=.htm | website = Box Office Mojo | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2015-10-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151016214448/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/people/chart/?view=Director&id=kenkwapis.htm&sort=maxtheaters&order=DESC&p=.htm}}</ref>。伊曼纽尔·利维认为本片目标观众是[[情人节|情人节]]出来约会的人群<ref name="SourceVTY" />。

电影上映首周在票房榜排名第三<ref name="SourceBOM" />，周末进账408万美元<ref name="Newspaper2">{{Cite news | date = 1997-02-12 | title = 'Dante's Peak' unable to slow down 'Star Wars' charge | page = 5 | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54493881/chicago-tribune/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200703140336/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54493881/chicago-tribune/ | deadurl = no | archive-date = 2020-07-03 | via = Newspapers.com | accessdate = 2020-11-01}} {{subscription required}}</ref><ref name="SourceHB3">{{Cite newspaper | title = Top Ten Films | archive-date = 2018-11-21 | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-712425.html | date = 1997-02-11 | newspaper = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181121020115/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-712425.html | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2018-11-21}} {{subscription required}}</ref>。影片的影院发行总收入只有1148万6880美元<ref name="SourceBOM" /><ref name="SourceBOM2">{{Cite web | title = The Beautician and the Beast (Weekly) | url = https://www.boxofficemojo.com/release/rl323257857/weekly/ | website = Box Office Mojo | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180630023638/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekly&id=beauticianandthebeast.htm | archive-date = 2018-06-30 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2018-06-30}}</ref>。2015年，[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]估算电影票价结合[[通货膨胀|通货膨胀]]后收入2254万8300美元<ref name="SourceBOMTheaters" />。《美容师与野兽》远未收回成本，属于[[票房炸弹|票房炸弹]]<ref name="SourceBOM" /><ref name="Source1" />。卓雪认为电影票房失败主要是因为上映时不巧遇到《[[星際大戰四部曲：曙光乍現|星球大战]]》特别[[數位修復|修复版]]强力竞争<ref name="SourceStarWars">{{Cite news | title = Fran Drescher Reflects on the Effect of 'The Beautician and the Beast' Opening the Same Weekend as 'Star Wars' | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-date = 2020-02-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200225150330/https://www.wfsb.com/fran-drescher-reflects-on-the-effect-of-the-beautician-and/video_66d66ceb-c0d0-50fa-a2d1-52ce5b6afe82.html | date = 2020-02-21 | work = WFSB | deadurl = no | url = https://www.wfsb.com/fran-drescher-reflects-on-the-effect-of-the-beautician-and/video_66d66ceb-c0d0-50fa-a2d1-52ce5b6afe82.html}}</ref>。

《美容师与野兽》的{{lang|en|[[家用录像系统|VHS]]}}录像带发行后于1998年3月21日登上《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|-{zh-cn:公告牌; zh-hk:告示牌; zh-tw:告示牌;}-]]》畅销榜第38位<ref name="SourceBillboardJournal1">{{Cite journal | date = 1998-03-21 | title = Top Video Sales | url = https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=2Q4EAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA94&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q&f=false | volume = 110 | issue = 12 | pages = 94 | access-date = 2020-11-01 | journal = [[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]}}</ref>。电影的{{lang|en|[[數碼多功能影音光碟|DVD]]}}在2003年6月24日发行，其中包含卓雪的评论音轨<ref name="SourceRT" /><ref name="SourceBBFC">{{Cite web | title = The Beautician and the Beast | url = https://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/beautician-and-beast-1970-2 | website = [[英國電影分級委員會|British Board of Film Classification]] | deadurl = yes | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | accessdate = 2018-07-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705101207/http://www.bbfc.co.uk/releases/beautician-and-beast-1970-2}}</ref><ref name="SourceCommentary">{{Cite interview | last = Drescher | first = Fran | subject-link = 法蘭·卓雪 | title = ''The Beautician and the Beast'' Audio Commentary | publisher = [[派拉蒙影業|Paramount Pictures]] | date = 2003-09-08}}</ref>。此外，本片还在[[亞馬遜影片|Prime影音]]提供线上发售<ref name="SourceTVGuide" />，并于2015年4到10月在{{lang|en|[[Netflix|Netflix]]}}发行[[流媒体|流媒体]]<ref>{{Cite journal | last = O'Neil | first = Lorena | date = 2015-04-21 | title = Netflix New Releases Coming in April 2015: 'Noah,' 'National Treasure,' 'Hot Fuzz' | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/netflix-new-releases-april-movies-790484 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200619214746/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/netflix-new-releases-april-movies-790484 | archive-date = 2020-06-19 | journal = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal | date = 2015-09-29 | title = Movies and TV Shows Leaving Netflix in October 2015 | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/netflix-leaving-october-2015-movies-tv-expiring-827882 | deadurl = no | archive-date = 2019-05-09 | journal = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190509031249/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/netflix-leaving-october-2015-movies-tv-expiring-827882 | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}</ref>。2020年{{lang|en|[[HBO_Max|HBO Max]]}}运营后同样提供流媒体观看<ref>{{Cite web | last = Patches | first = Matt | date = 2020-05-27 | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.polygon.com/2020/5/27/21271224/hbo-max-tv-shows-movies-full-list-dc-batman-superman-warner-bros-criterion-anime | title = Nearly every movie and show now on HBO Max | website = [[Polygon|Polygon]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201001163114/https://www.polygon.com/2020/5/27/21271224/hbo-max-tv-shows-movies-full-list-dc-batman-superman-warner-bros-criterion-anime | archive-date = 2020-10-01}}</ref>。卓雪在2020年接受采访时称，影片一直在为派拉蒙影业营收，而且已经开始发展续作<ref name="SourceStarWars" />。她还称，派拉蒙影业总裁[[雪莉·兰辛|雪莉·兰辛]]透露本片家用视频和电视收视成绩一直很好，足以证明这是能够经受时间考验的作品<ref name="2020Source2">{{Cite web | title = Fran Drescher Is Back to Help You Through These Dark Times | url = http://www.newnownext.com/fran-drescher-on-indebted-nanny-musical-updates/03/2020/ | last = Rudolph | first = Christopher | date = 2020-03-31 | website = NewNowNext.com | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200420020939/http://www.newnownext.com/fran-drescher-on-indebted-nanny-musical-updates/03/2020/ | archive-date = 2020-04-20}}</ref>。

== 专业评价 ==
影评人对《美容师与野兽》普遍评价不佳<ref name="SourceRT" /><ref name="SourceComplex" /><ref name="SourceRT2">{{Cite web | title = Critic Reviews | archive-date = 2018-07-04 | website = Rotten Tomatoes | url = https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beautician_and_the_beast/reviews | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180704002516/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/beautician_and_the_beast/reviews/ | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[罗杰·伊伯特|罗杰·伊伯特]]虽然认可女主角的魅力，但觉得观众无法对乔伊产生共鸣，因为“我们根本不觉得她会彷徨、担忧或脆弱”<ref name="SourceRE" />。[[MTV新闻|MTV新闻]]（{{lang|en|MTV News}}）刊登埃里克·斯尼德（{{lang|en|Eric Snider}}）的文章，批评影片人物发展和缺乏幽默的剧情<ref name="SourceMTVNews" />。《[[芝加哥論壇報|芝加哥論壇報]]》的[[吉恩·西斯克|吉恩·西斯克]]（{{lang|en|Gene Siskel}}）认为剧本表现欠佳，恶搞《音乐之声》的情节尽显愚蠢<ref name="SourceCT">{{Cite news | title = It Takes An Hour For `Dante's Peak' To Start Cooking | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1997-02-07-9702070247-story.html | last = Siskel | first = Gene | date = 1997-02-07 | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200308183959/https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1997-02-07-9702070247-story.html | archive-date = 2020-03-08}}</ref>。不过，《[[电视指南_(美国杂志)|电视指南]]》的[[梅特兰·麦克唐纳|梅特兰·麦克唐纳]]（{{lang|en|Maitland McDonagh}}）和{{lang|en|[[IGN|IGN]]}}网站的阿诺德·布伦伯格（{{lang|en|Arnold T. Blumberg}}）认为，《美容师与野兽》的观影过程颇为愉快，既不至让人感到冒犯，内容也足够轻松<ref name="SourceTVGuide" /><ref name="SourceIGN" />。凯莉·里基（{{lang|en|Carrie Rickey}}）在《[[費城詢問報|費城詢問報]]》发文，称本片就像风味小吃，把几乎所有童话恶搞个遍，时不时会有很没脸没皮的风趣桥段<ref name="Newspaper1">{{Cite news | date = 1997-02-16 | last = Rickey | first = Carrie | title = New and Noteworthy: Box-office hits | newspaper = [[費城詢問報|The Philadelphia Inquirer]] | page = F2 | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54493816/the-philadelphia-inquirer/ | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200701181434/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54493816/the-philadelphia-inquirer/ | archive-date = 2020-07-01 | via = Newspapers.com}} {{subscription required}}</ref>。

评论员批评电影太像情景喜剧<ref name="SourceTBS" /><ref name="Book5" /><ref name="NewspaperAugust162">{{Cite news | last = Arnold | first = William | date = 1997-02-08 | title = 'Beautician' resembles TV sitcom | work = The Town Talk | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54493758/the-town-talk/ | page = C7 | access-date = 2020-11-01 | via = Newspapers.com | archivedate = 2020-07-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200701120954/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54493758/the-town-talk/}} {{subscription required}}</ref>，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》刊登斯蒂芬·霍尔顿（{{lang|en|Stephen Holden}}）的文章，称卡皮斯和格拉夫对素材的提炼还不足以支撑长片电影需要<ref name="SourcePotential">{{Cite news | title = A Dictator Who Has Potential | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1997/02/07/movies/a-dictator-who-has-potential.html | last = Holden | first = Stephen | date = 1997-02-07 | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201004022512/https://www.nytimes.com/1997/02/07/movies/a-dictator-who-has-potential.html | archive-date = 2020-10-04 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | page = C12}}</ref>。[[丽莎·施瓦茨鲍姆|丽莎·施瓦茨鲍姆]]（{{lang|en|Lisa Schwarzbaum}}）在《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》发文，称本片和同年的《[[傻瓜跑进来|傻瓜跑进来]]》（{{lang|en|''Fools Rush In''}}）失败原因类似，故事本身或多或少有些干货不足，但却都很自命不凡<ref name="SourceEW" />。还有评论认为乔伊基本上就是卓雪在《天才保姆》中角色的翻版<ref name="Book5" /><ref name="NewspaperAugust161">{{Cite news | date = 1997-02-07 | title = Screenings: New Releases | page = 2B | work = Lincoln Journal Star | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54493680/lincoln-journal-star/ | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200701034047/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/54493680/lincoln-journal-star/ | archive-date = 2020-07-01 | via = Newspapers.com | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}{{subscription required}}</ref>，堪称[[浪漫喜剧|浪漫喜剧]]类型片的负面典型<ref name="SourceComplex" /><ref name="SourceCSM">{{Cite web | title = The Beautician and the Beast | url = https://www.commonsensemedia.org/movie-reviews/the-beautician-and-the-beast | last = Montgomery | first = Grace | date = 2015-04-15 | website = Common Sense Media | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201008084043/https://www.commonsensemedia.org/movie-reviews/the-beautician-and-the-beast | archive-date = 2020-10-08 | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}</ref>。《[[圣地亚哥读者报|圣地亚哥读者报]]》（''{{lang|en|San Diego Reader}}''）的邓肯·谢泼德（{{lang|en|Duncan Shepherd}}）批评《美容师与野兽》的剧情不过是将《妮诺契卡》性别倒转，处处显得廉价<ref name="SourceSDR" />。[[常识媒体|常识媒体]]（{{lang|en|Common Sense Media}}）刊登格蕾丝·蒙哥马利（{{lang|en|Grace Montgomery}}）的评价，称影片是过时的90年代浪漫喜剧，过于依赖陈辞滥调和老套俗見<ref name="SourceCSM" />。2015年，“精炼29”（{{lang|en|Refinery29}}）网站的艾琳·唐纳利（{{lang|en|Erin Donnelly}}）将乔伊和鲍里斯列入最缺乏化学反应的30对浪漫喜剧情侣<ref name="SourceRefine2">{{Cite web | title = 30 Random Rom-Com Couples That Didn't Quite Work | url = https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/2015/08/92765/weird-romantic-comedy-couples | last = Donnelly | first = Erin | date = 2015-08-24 | website = Refinery29}}</ref>。但劳伦·勒藤（{{lang|en|Lauren Le Vine}}）同年也在该网站发文，声称《美容师与野兽》堪称经典并赞扬男女主角的化学反应<ref name="SourceRefine">{{Cite web | title = Here's Everything Coming To Netflix In April | url = https://www.refinery29.com/en-us/2015/04/84043/new-on-netflix-april-2015 | last = Le Vine | first = Lauren | date = 2015-04-02 | website = Refinery29 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160201151043/http://www.refinery29.com/2015/04/84043/new-on-netflix-april-2015 | archive-date = 2016-02-01}}</ref>。

卓雪的演出评价不一。伊曼纽尔·利维称赞乔伊“随和、风趣而讨喜”，就是40岁的女演员演天真少女有点不妥。利维觉得她的噪音独特，结合犹太人特色举止让人想到[[范妮·布莱斯|范妮·布莱斯]]（{{lang|en|Fanny Brice}}）和[[芭芭拉·史翠珊|芭芭拉·史翠珊]]。<ref name="SourceVTY" />约翰·彼得拉基斯（{{lang|en|John Petrakis}}）在《芝加哥论坛报》发文，称赞本片有20世纪50年代电影中那种“战后的天真”风味，在他看来，乔伊的形象，特别是“蓬松的波浪发型、浓重的妆粉、花哨的衣装和异乎寻常的嗓音”，让人想起[[茱蒂·霍利德|茱蒂·霍利德]]<ref name="SourceBeauty">{{Cite news | title = Beauty Of Fran Drescher's `Beautician' In The Comedic Writing | accessdate = 2020-11-01 | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1997-02-07-9702070244-story.html | last = Petrakis | first = John | date = 1997-02-07 | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | archive-date = 2018-07-05 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180705063316/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1997-02-07/entertainment/9702070244_1_beautician-joy-miller-beast}}</ref>。《[[德瑟雷特新闻报|德瑟雷特新闻报]]》（''{{lang|en|Deseret News}}''）的杰夫·维奇（{{lang|en|Jeff Vice}}）认为，男女主角让人想到[[尤·伯連納|尤·伯連納]]和[[狄波拉·嘉|狄波拉·嘉]]，但表现远远不及<ref name="SourceDesert" />；埃里克·斯尼德批评卓雪塑造的人物就像地狱版玛丽·波平斯（{{lang|en|Mary Poppins}}），笑起来像猪一样哼哼作响<ref name="SourceMTVNews" />。许多评论对卓雪的噪音不以为然<ref name="SourceTBS" /><ref name="SourceRE" /><ref name="SourceLAT" />，梅特兰·麦克唐纳觉得她的“鼻音能震碎水晶”，但估计粉丝会喜欢如此演出<ref name="SourceTVGuide" />。卓雪获[[第18届金酸莓奖|第18届金酸莓奖]][[金酸莓獎最差女主角|最差女主角奖]]提名，所幸没有获奖<ref name="SourceRazzy">{{Cite web | title = 1997 Archive | archive-date = 2016-04-13 | accessdate = 2016-04-13 | url = http://razzies.com/asp/content/XcNewsPlus.asp?cmd=view&articleid=37 | last = Wilson | first = John | date = 1998-03-22 | website = [[金酸莓獎|Golden Raspberry Awards]] | deadurl = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160413062702/http://razzies.com/asp/content/XcNewsPlus.asp?cmd=view&articleid=37}}</ref>。

影评人对道尔顿的表演同样褒贬不一。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》刊登丽塔·肯普利（{{lang|en|Rita Kempley}}）的文章，称赞道尔顿的[[坎普风|坎普风]]演出<ref name="SourceTWP">{{Cite news | title = The Beautician and the Beast' | deadurl = no | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/review97/beauticianandthebeastkemp.htm | last = Kempley | first = Rita | date = 1997-02-07 | newspaper = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201004022513/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/review97/beauticianandthebeastkemp.htm | archive-date = 2020-10-04 | accessdate = 2020-10-04}}</ref>，杰夫·维奇认可他的面部表情及细致入微的变化<ref name="SourceDesert" />。史蒂芬·亨特觉得道尔德虽然成功塑造和蔼可亲的人物，但电影整体表现太差，无法让他星途更进一步<ref name="SourceTBS" />。约翰·安德森（{{lang|en|John Anderson}}）在《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》发文，认可男主角的喜剧演出，但感觉所有人物在卓雪旁边都显得僵硬<ref name="SourceLAT">{{Cite news | title = 'Beautician and the Beast': 'King and I' Meets 'Nanny' | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1997-02-07-ca-26189-story.html | last = Anderson | first = John | date = 1997-02-07 | newspaper = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180630023638/http://articles.latimes.com/1997-02-07/entertainment/ca-26189_1_fran-drescher | archive-date = 2018-06-30 | accessdate = 2020-11-01}}</ref>。梅特兰·麦克唐纳批评道尔顿过于严肃，如果不是选他主演，电影可能会更加轻松愉快<ref name="SourceTVGuide" />。《[[林肯星报|林肯星报]]》的文章也对道尔顿评价不佳，觉得他皱起眉头就像便秘，所以在片中只适合一直坐着不动<ref name="NewspaperAugust161" />。

